<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1448054-i-m-puzzled-by-references-to-a-key-to-the">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I'm puzzled by references to a key to the chapel that was found in Lorrimer's pocket, presumably replaced there by the murderer. But at the scene of the second murder Domenica tells Dalgliesh that she didn't ask Lorrimer to return his chapel key to her when she broke up with him. The murderer presumably had his own chapel key. So were there 3 copies plus the original? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
