<span id="freeTextContainer7398492610153644092">This was another great twisty and turny Dalgliesh book by P.D. James. It seems with each instalment of the series it gets even more complex. Which I find greatly enjoyable.<br/><br/>Like most James readers I watched the series, so as I was reading the book the series played through my head.<br/><br/>And I am looking forward to the next book.<br/><br/></span>

          </span>
