  <span id="freeText16157241106706686955" style="display:none">A forensic investigator who works in a medical examiner's office is found killed inside the locked building. Dalgliesh and his team start sifting through the clues and suspects. Can they figure it out before someone else gets killed?<br /><br />Very well-written. Great police procedural. One of my favorite authors.</span>
